00:44:35.600 --> 00:44:37.240
Ahora depende de ti.

00:44:42.310 --> 00:44:44.339
¡Oye, espera por mí!

00:44:45.180 --> 00:44:46.240
Oye.

00:44:47.709 --> 00:44:48.749
Tae Hee!

