00:50:07.100 --> 00:50:08.100
Hola, Sr. Lee.

00:50:08.269 --> 00:50:09.830
Sí, Sr. Kang.

00:50:13.939 --> 00:50:15.010
La cosa es,

00:50:16.470 --> 00:50:19.939
